{"analytics_identifier":"EA58","base_path":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency","content_id":"e8fae147-6232-4163-a3f1-1c15b755a8a4","description":"We pay out over £2 billion each year to support a thriving farming and food sector, supporting agricultural and rural communities to create a better place to live. RPA is an executive agency, sponsored by the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs , supported by 1 public body .","details":{"acronym":"RPA","alternative_format_contact_email":"Webmaster.RPA@rpa.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We pay out over £2 billion each year to support a thriving farming and food sector, supporting agricultural and rural communities to create a better place to live.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Rural Payments Agency\">RPA</abbr> is an executive agency, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-environment-food-rural-affairs\">Department for Environment, Food &amp; Rural Affairs</a>, supported by <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations#rural-payments-agency\">1 public body</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-environment-food-rural-affairs","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Rural Payments <br/>Agency"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency/about/equality-and-diversity","title":"Equality and diversity"},{"href":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency/about/our-energy-use","title":"Our energy use"},{"href":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/rural-payments-agency/about/procurement","title":"Procurement at RPA"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Blog post","href":"https://defrafarming.blog.gov.uk/2026/05/06/get-ready-to-apply-for-sfi26","image":{"alt_text":"A laptop screen showing the \"Land summary\" screen on the Rural Payments service","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a06f12397000cb6073e4e8e/s712_getreadysfi.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a06f12397000cb6073e4e8f/s465_getreadysfi.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a06f123ee62840dba48a337/getreadysfi.png"},"public_updated_at":"2025-05-06T00:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>In this post, we tell you more about the first application window for the Sustainable Farming Incentive (SFI) offer in 2026.</p>\n</div>","title":"Get ready to apply for SFI26"},{"document_type":"Blog post","href":"https://defrafarming.blog.gov.uk/2026/03/19/the-2026-capital-grants-offer/","image":{"alt_text":"A farming landscape with some shrubs in the foreground, and hills and fields in the background","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c27b40b920af63be1c774c/s712_featured_CG.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c27b40d588c92c483e4c75/s465_featured_CG.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c27b407e02b81c0d1c774a/featured_CG.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-19T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>When the Capital Grants offer opens in July, £225 million will be available to support farmers, land managers and rural businesses to deliver environmental improvements across England.</p>\n</div>","title":"The 2026 Capital Grants offer"},{"document_type":"Blog post","href":"https://ruralpayments.blog.gov.uk/2026/03/18/countryside-stewardship-and-environmental-stewardship-revenue-claims-are-open-for-2026/","image":{"alt_text":"View of rural landscape with farms and hills","high_resol